 at the Asian Rifle and Pistol Championships in Indonesia in January, and again by two places at the ISSF Final Olympic Qualification Championship in Brazil three months later.\", \"from\": 940, \"to\": 1146, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 978, \"end\": 983, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4381699700836463e-19, \"text\": \"Asian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 1018, \"end\": 1027, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesia_national_badminton_team\", \"score\": 0.9991958431077065, \"rank\": 0.000788569900201884, \"text\": \"Indonesia\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesia_national_badminton_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesia_national_badminton_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1120, \"end\": 1126, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9918217097398356, \"rank\": 0.006903206185139896, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one spot\", \"from\": 962, \"to\": 970}, {\"ngram\": \"Pistol Championships\", \"from\": 994, \"to\": 1014}, {\"ngram\": \"January\", \"from\": 1031, \"to\": 1038}, {\"ngram\": \"two places\", \"from\": 1053, \"to\": 1063}, {\"ngram\": \"the ISSF Final Olympic Qualification Championship\", \"from\": 1067, \"to\": 1116}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She is currently in Xiamen, China for a short break and received the confirmation via e-mail on June 14.\", \"from\": 1148, \"to\": 1252, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1168, \"end\": 1174, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xiamen\", \"score\": 0.9999999999790816, \"rank\": 2.103410808504435