: 1572}, {\"ngram\": \"my coach\", \"from\": 1574, \"to\": 1582}, {\"ngram\": \"the next competition\", \"from\": 1636, \"to\": 1656}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nevertheless, she found the qualifying campaign \\\"an incredibly challenging journey\\\" and thanked the Singapore Shooting Association (SSA), coach Lee Do-hee, the spexScholarship programme and sports psychologist Harry Lim for their \\\"invaluable support\\\", particularly in maintaining her mental well-being.\", \"from\": 1660, \"to\": 1962, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1760, \"end\": 1769, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3844854497747484e-21, \"text\": \"Singapore\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\"}, {\"begin\": 1792, \"end\": 1795, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Social_Security_Administration\", \"score\": 0.9992083905494241, \"rank\": 0.0004927643713008585, \"text\": \"SSA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Social_Security_Administration\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Social_Security_Administration\"}, {\"begin\": 1804, \"end\": 1807, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_E._Lee\", \"score\": 0.980719185309532, \"rank\": 0.01965577749453049, \"text\": \"Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_E._Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_E._Lee\"}, {\"begin\": 1870, \"end\": 1879, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harry_Lim\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Harry Lim\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harry_Lim\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harry_Lim\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the qualifying campaign\", \"from\": 1684, \"to\": 1707}, {\"ngram\": \"the spexScholarship programme\", \"from\": 1816, \"to\": 1845}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 1850, \"to\": 1856}, {\"ngram\": \"their \\\"invaluable support\", \"from\": 1884, \"to\": 1909}, {\"ngram\": \"her mental well-being\", \"from\": 1940, \"to\": 1961}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said: \\\"They all played a crucial role in helping me secure this quota.\", \"from\": 1964, \"to\": 2038, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a crucial role\", \"from\": 1991, \"to\": 2005}, {\"ngram\": \"this quota\", \"from\": 2027, \"to\": 2037}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I faced many setbacks and disappointments, but I kept pushing forward.\\\"\", \"from\": 2039, \"to\": 2110, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"many setbacks\", \"from\": 2047, \"to\": 2060}, {\"ngram\": \"disappointments\", \"from\": 2065, \"to\": 2080}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ultimately, her efforts paid off as the ranking points accumulated from those competitions allowed her to overtake several contenders - including compatriot and 2016 Olympian Teo Shun Xie - to punch her ticket to Paris.\", \"from\": 2112, \"to\": 2331, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2278, \"end\": 2286, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999898191163, \"rank\": 1.0180949670698446e-08, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 2287, \"end\": 2299, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Teo_Shun_Xie\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Teo Shun Xie\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Teo_Shun_Xie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Teo_Shun_Xie\"}, {\"begin\": 2325, \"end\": 2330, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999996821316, \"rank\": 3.1768706710498944e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her efforts\", \"from\": 2124, \"to\": 2135}, {\"ngram\": \"the ranking points\", \"from\": 2148, \"to\": 2166}, {\"ngram\": \"those competitions\", \"from\": 2184, \"to\": 2202}, {\"ngram\": \"several contenders\", \"from\": 2227, \"to\": 2245}, {\"ngram\": \"compatriot\", \"from\": 2258, \"to\": 2268}, {\"ngram\": \"her ticket\", \"from\": 2311, \"to\": 2321}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Emboldened by this, Teh wants to be the first Singaporean shooter to win an Olympic medal.\", \"from\": 2333, \"to\": 2423, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2379, \"end\": 2390, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"score\": 0.9983815247249158, \"rank\": 0.0016210989837636537, \"text\": \"Singaporean\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Teh\", \"from\": 2353, \"to\": 2356}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic medal\", \"from\": 2406, \"to\": 2422}]}, {\"sentence\": \"National pistol coach Lee, a South Korean who has worked with Olympic champion Kim Jang-mi and several World Cup medallists, credited Teh for her positivity and mentality.\", \"from\": 2425, \"to\": 2596, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2447, \"end\": 2450, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_E._Lee\", \"score\": 0.980719185309532, \"rank\": 0.01965577749453049, \"text\": \"Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_E._Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_E._Lee\"}, {\"begin\": 2460, \"end\": 2466, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"score\": 0.9999874714501792, \"rank\": 1.252636309058234e-05, \"text\": \"Korean\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\"}, {\"begin\": 2504, \"end\": 2515, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Jang-mi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kim Jang-mi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Jang-mi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Jang-mi\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"National pistol coach\", \"from\": 2425, \"to\": 2446}, {\"ngram\": \"several World Cup medallists\", \"from\": 2520, \"to\": 2548}, {\"ngram\": \"Teh\", \"from\": 2559, \"to\": 2562}, {\"ngram\": \"her positivity\", \"from\": 2567, \"to\": 2581}, {\"ngram\": \"mentality\", \"from\": 2586, \"to\": 2595}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Having worked with her over two stints in 2019-20 and from 2023, she told ST: \\\"Xiu Hong is a positive individual who is willing to take on challenging training so that I could bring out her strengths.\", \"from\": 2598, \"to\": 2798, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2677, \"end\": 2680, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xiu\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Xiu\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xiu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xiu\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two stints\", \"from\": 2626, \"to\": 2636}, {\"ngram\": \"ST\", \"from\": 2672, \"to\": 2674}, {\"ngram\": \"a positive individual\", \"from\": 2689, \"to\": 2710}, {\"ngram\": \"challenging training\", \"from\": 2737, \"to\": 2757}, {\"ngram\": \"her strengths\", \"from\": 2784, \"to\": 2797}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The mental game is one of the important parts of shooting and I believe the strong trust and connection between the athlete and the coach is important.\", \"from\": 2800, \"to\": 2952, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The mental game\", \"from\": 2801, \"to\": 2816}, {\"ngram\": \"the important parts\", \"from\": 2827, \"to\": 2846}, {\"ngram\": \"shooting\", \"from\": 2850, \"to\": 2858}, {\"ngram\": \"the strong trust\", \"from\": 2873, \"to\": 2889}, {\"ngram\": \"connection\", \"from\": 2894, \"to\": 2904}, {\"ngram\": \"the athlete\", \"from\": 2913, \"to\": 2924}, {\"ngram\": \"the coach\", \"from\": 2929, \"to\": 2938}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These factors have contributed to her rapid growth and improvement in a short period of time.\", \"from\": 2953, \"to\": 3046, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"These factors\", \"from\": 2953, \"to\": 2966}, {\"ngram\": \"her rapid growth\", \"from\": 2987, \"to\": 3003}, {\"ngram\": \"improvement\", \"from\": 3008, \"to\": 3019}, {\"ngram\": \"a short period\", \"from\": 3023, \"to\": 3037}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 3041, \"to\": 3045}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"One of her technical skills is her excellent trigger control.\", \"from\": 3048, \"to\": 3110, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her technical skills\", \"from\": 3056, \"to\": 3076}, {\"ngram\": \"her excellent trigger control\", \"from\": 3080, \"to\": 3109}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If she gains more experience and learns to alleviate competition anxiety, she has the potential to further excel as an athlete.\\\"\", \"from\": 3111, \"to\": 3239, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more experience\", \"from\": 3124, \"to\": 3139}, {\"ngram\": \"competition anxiety\", \"from\": 3164, \"to\": 3183}, {\"ngram\": \"the potential\", \"from\": 3193, \"to\": 3206}, {\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 3227, \"to\": 3237}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Teh's qualification means that Singapore shooting will continue its tradition of being represented at every Olympics since Seoul 1988.\", \"from\": 3241, \"to\": 3375, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3272, \"end\": 3281, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3844854497747484e-21, \"text\": \"Singapore\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\"}, {\"begin\": 3364, \"end\": 3374, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1988_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999997746895387, \"rank\": 2.2531033624288783e-07, \"text\": \"Seoul 1988\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1988_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1988_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Teh's qualification\", \"from\": 3241, \"to\": 3260}, {\"ngram\": \"its tradition\", \"from\": 3305, \"to\": 3318}, {\"ngram\": \"every Olympics\", \"from\": 3343, \"to\": 3357}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SSA president Michael Vaz expressed confidence that the streak would not be broken.\", \"from\": 3377, \"to\": 3460, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3377, \"end\": 3380, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Social_Security_Administration\", \"score\": 0.9992083905494241, \"rank\": 0.0004927643713008585, \"text\": \"SSA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Social_Security_Administration\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Social_Security_Administration\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"confidence\", \"from\": 3413, \"to\": 3423}, {\"ngram\": \"the streak\", \"from\": 3429, \"to\": 3439}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Vaz, who is pushing for an eight-lane finals range to be built here, said: \\\"We have had to fight for ranking points instead of a quota for the Olympics through finals events as we do not have a finals range to practise for that.\", \"from\": 3462, \"to\": 3690, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an eight-lane finals\", \"from\": 3486, \"to\": 3506}, {\"ngram\": \"ranking points\", \"from\": 3563, \"to\": 3577}, {\"ngram\": \"a quota\", \"from\": 3589, \"to\": 3596}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3601, \"to\": 3613}, {\"ngram\": \"finals events\", \"from\": 3622, \"to\": 3635}, {\"ngram\": \"a finals\", \"from\": 3654, \"to\": 3662}, {\"ngram\": \"range\", \"from\": 3663, \"to\": 3668}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The finals events that produce medals are a different format and we have been faring badly in these.\",